

MARAHIL

   root word: [66]dahil

   ma·rá·hil
   perhaps, possibly

   Marahil nagkasakit siya.
   Perhaps he/she got sick.

   Marahil pagod lang siya.
   Perhaps she/he is merely tired.

   A more colloquial Tagalog word for ‘maybe’ is [67]bakâ.
   Bakâ pagod siya.
   Maybe she/he is tired.

KAHULUGAN SA TAGALOG

   maráhil: nagsasaad ng posibilidad
